[[Denmark]] is a [[Scandinavia]]n country in [[Europe]] located on the [[56th parallel north]]. Denmark is located at a zone where air masses from a diverse range of regions congregate, giving it its temperate climate.Though Denmark’s average temperature is only 7.7 degrees.
