'''Sibilan''', as depicted in ''[[Bayan Ko (TV series)]]'', is a fictional province where [[Lagros, Sibilan|Lagros]] are.
==Premise== {{Main|Bayan Ko (TV series)}} Lagros' newly elected mayor, Joseph Santiago, discovers that a bunch of wayward employees have turned the municipal hall into a boarding house and, worse, have been making under the table deals. His efforts to fight corruption are blocked by a political dynasty led by Governor Antonio Rubio and Congressman Anton Rubio.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/video/shows/bayanko |title=Bayan Ko &#124; GMA News TV Shows &#124; Videos and Episodes &#124; GMA News Online |publisher=Gmanetwork.com |date= |accessdate=2013-10-15}}</ref>
